results.title: Personalized Cutting Board
results.description:
These beautiful cutting boards make the perfect gift for any wedding, anniversary or housewarming. Personalize this gift with a name and the date to remember.

Choose from the following cutting board options:
- Walnut 12 X 9 IN 
- Walnut 10.5 IN Round with Juice Groove 
- Walnut 14 X 5.5 IN Paddle Board 
- Acacia Wood 14 X 6 IN Paddle Board with leather strap
- Acacia Wood 18.25 X 10.5 IN with Handle and Rope Hanger
- Bamboo 10 X 8 IN board
- Bamboo 13 X 10 IN board
- Bamboo 16 X 12 IN board with Juice Groove
- Bamboo Premium 18 X 12 IN chopping board 

All items are made to order. We engrave each order exactly as it is received, so please be sure to double check spelling and date information you've provided. Because these are personalized items we will not be able to accept returns or exchanges for errors on the customers part. 

All boards are made from all natural wood and as a result each board will vary slightly in color based on the natural properties of each piece. 

Enter the first and last names and date for personalization.
